  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:0",
      "text": "Engine 维护中央 job queue，并把 tasks 分配给 farm 上的 servers。它也是 blades 上报 status information 的中央 clearinghouse。Engine 还会交付 Tractor Dashboard 所需的 web content。Usage: tractor-engine [options]（用法）",
      "ascii_letters": 123,
      "cjk_chars": 28
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:9",
      "text": "--configdir=path",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:13",
      "text": "指定包含 Tractor configuration files 的目录，默认值为 /var/spool/tractor/config。Tractor-engine 也会检查环境变量 TRACTOR_CONFIG。",
      "ascii_letters": 72,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:14",
      "text": "--log=filename",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:15",
      "text": "指定用于记录 engine 自身 diagnostics 的 filename。默认值为 stderr。",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:19",
      "text": "将 logging level 从 NOTICE 提高到 INFO。",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:23",
      "text": "将 logging level 从 NOTICE 降低到 SEVERE。",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:25",
      "text": "将日志 logging level 提高到 DEBUG。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:27",
      "text": "将日志 logging level 提高到 TRACE。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:28",
      "text": "--httpdebug",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:29",
      "text": "记录传入的 http requests",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:30",
      "text": "--nshippers=n",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:34",
      "text": "设置为处理 i/o 而创建的 thread 数量（default=ncores）。",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:35",
      "text": "--maxdispatch=n",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:39",
      "text": "限制并发 dispatches（以及 license use）。",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:41",
      "text": "指定 engine 的 inbound connection port（default=80）。",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:42",
      "text": "--port=addr:port",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:43",
      "text": "将 inbound listener port 限制到由 address 给出的 network interface，并使用 port number port。默认情况下，engine 会在所有 interfaces 的 port 80 上监听 connections。示例用法：--port=8080 或 --port=127.0.0.1:9999",
      "ascii_letters": 95,
      "cjk_chars": 29
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:44",
      "text": "--supersede",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:47",
      "text": "使新重启的 engine 立即进入 pause all dispatching 状态。因此，在管理员使用 Dashboard 的 Gears->Admin 标签页中的红色 play 按钮手动重新启用 dispatching 之前，不会有新的 commands 分配给 blades。即使 engine 以 --paused mode 重启，job database 中标记为 still-active 的任何现有 commands 仍会被新 engine 视为 active。在这些情况下，仍在运行的 blades 会与新 engine 通信，以确认这些 commands 中哪些实际仍在运行。",
      "ascii_letters": 151,
      "cjk_chars": 95
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:48",
      "text": "--startupdelay=n",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:49",
      "text": "Engine 在 startup 时简单 sleep n 秒。",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:51",
      "text": "Engine 在 system service mode 中自动进入 background。",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:52",
      "text": "--pidfile=filename",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:53",
      "text": "在 daemon mode 中，将最终 PID 写入 filename。",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "edb93fc31a:55",
      "text": "不要覆盖默认的 SEGV/BUS handlers。",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    }
  ],
